    <text>
        <front>
            <div type="summary">
                <p>
                    Letter from V. Sackville-West to Leonard in which she introduces Mr. Jullian as suitable artist to illustrate <title> The Edwardians</title>
                  </p>
            </div>
        </front>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <placeName>
                          Sissinghurst Castle, Kent
                        </placeName>
                        <date when="1946-07-15">
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>
                            <persName> Leonard </persName>
                        </addrLine>
                        <addrLine>
                            <!-- recipient's address (add <addrLine>s as required) -->
                        </addrLine>
                    </address>
                    <salute>
                        My dear <persName>Leonard</persName>,
                    </salute>
                </opener>
                <p>
                  This is to introduce Mr. <persName>Jullian</persName> who is
                  a French artist and wants to discuss with you
                  the possibility of illustrating <title>The Edwardians</title>.
                  I gave him a letter for <persName>John Lehman</persName> some time
                  ago but <persName>John</persName> told him that he was leaving the
                  Press and as Mr. <persName>Jullian</persName> was just going back to
                  France the matter was left in abeyance. He has
                  now returned to England and will no doubt bring
                  this <choice><sic>nore</sic><corr>note</corr></choice> in person. I have never met him but
                  I have seen some of his drawings which are
                  really delightful and would be most suitable
                  for <title>The Edwardians</title>.
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>
                        Yours ever,
                    </salute>
                    <signed> <persName>Vita</persName> </signed>
                    <seg>
                        <!-- post scriptum -->
                    </seg>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
